text.textblock: Research, Engineering and Development Advisory Committee Flight Service Technology Subcommittee Notice of Meeting; Correction

summary.textblock: On page 59 FR 646 in the issue of Wednesday, January 5, 1994, make the following correction: The time published for the January 28 Research, Engineering and Development Advisory Committee, Flight Service Technology Subcommittee meeting was 10 a.m. This should be changed to read 9:30 a.m.

signjob.textblock: Executive Director, Research, Engineering and Development Advisory Committee.
